fielddes: Stock company number, which equals bq_legal_entity_id
Unique ID assigned by BQ to the Organization.
TICKER of the Organization if it is publicly listed.

Link to the Organization's primary website. A company's website is not usually included in the regulatory filings, but BQ uses alternative methods to identify these links, which may result in occasional inaccuracies.
Unique ID of the event (amalgamation of the Delaware company number, date of event, trigger, and event type).
IDs of the new stock class series created by the event (bq_stock_class_series_id), if relevant; separated by semi-column
New stock group (typically associated with a new filing); or Change in tax year
Change in authorized shares of a stock class series; Change in total assets of a stock group; Change in issued shares of a stock group; Introduction of a new stock class series
Code for Change in authorized shares of a stock class series; Change in total assets of a stock group; Change in issued shares of a stock group; Introduction of a new stock class series
IDs of the stock class series being affected (bq_stock_class_series_id), if relevant; separated by semi-column
IDs of the most recent stock classes before the event, if relevant; separated by semi-column
IDs of the stock classes created by the event, if relevant; separated by semi-column
ID of the most recent stock group before the event, if relevant
ID of the stock group created by the event, if relevant
New stock group date (in which case, the event date is set as bq_stock_group_begin_date of the new stock group); or Change in tax year (in which case, the event date is set as Jan 1 of that year)
Date and time data was last received from the State of Delaware for this company
